[pink_dye]timber181的皮肤合集[pink_dye]


此为转载哟！

今天为大家搬运了5个皮肤，希望大家能够喜欢哟！！
顺便把介绍也搬过来～

名称：
Ombre Hair Girl With Beanie And Sweater
介绍：
Dute girl with teal sweater, leather boots, ombre hair, blue eyes and a beanie



名称：
Cute Girl With Striped Dress And Ombre Hair (Alex skin)
介绍：
Ombre haired girl, with striped dress, a pink bow and pink shoes. Also an alex skin.


名称：
Teal Sweater Girl with flowers in hair :)
介绍：
Teal sweater and flowers in her hair and high wasted shorts.


名称：
Beanie Girl with pink sweater (Alex Skin)
介绍：
Cute girl with a beanie, boots, blue jeans, pink sweater and a grey shirt under it.


名称：
Rainbow girl with backpack
介绍：
A girl with rainbow hair, a hat, black shoes and a blue backpack.


注：
皮肤为1.7.2使用！！

我很少转载，所以如果能够让我补充的请回复！！
金粒和人气呀！！！
